description:
Earn cash back when you buy your favorite brands. Install the app now to see how much you can save on groceries this week!

All you need to do is follow these simple steps:
1. Browse the offers that are updated every Thursday
2. Buy the products from any store
3. Take a photo of your receipt to redeem your deal
4. Earn cash back!

Once your account reaches $20 in savings, we’ll mail you a check!

No more:
- flipping through massive coupon booklets to find good deals
- snipping lots of little coupons
- remembering to take coupons to the store
- arguing with the cashier and holding up the rest of the line!

Best of all, you can purchase the products on offer at any grocery store including Walmart, Kroger, Costco, Target, Safeway, Supervalu, CVS, Publix, and all the rest!

Check out what others have to say:
- "Say goodbye to clipping coupons" - Global TV
- "App makes couponing easy" - Windsor Star
- "Snap, send, get money — it’s new-age couponing" - Vancouver Sun

Here is what our members have to say:

releaseNotes:
This update is for a minor performance improvement. 

In case you missed it: 

Our last update introduced Stars! This new feature let’s you star offers as you scroll through your list so you can: 

- easily keep track of the offers you want to redeem
- view your starred offers on their own shortlist
- see the grand total of how much you’ll save each week!

Many of you have told us this is a feature you’d love to see, so thanks for the great idea and we hope you like it as much as we do!
